'''戴琪'''{{r|wj201210}}（{{lang-en|Katherine Chi Tai}}<ref name=fp>{{Cite web|date=|title=Employee Profile of Katherine Chi Tai - General Attorney|language=en-US|work=|url=https://www.federalpay.org/employees/office-of-the-us-trade-representative/tai-katherine-chi|access-date=2020-12-11|via=FederalPay.org|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212205316/https://www.federalpay.org/employees/office-of-the-us-trade-representative/tai-katherine-chi|dead-url=no}}</ref>，'''凱瑟琳·琪·戴'''，{{bd|1974年|3月18日|}}）是一名[[台裔美國人|台裔美國人]]出身的贸易律师，現任[[美國貿易代表|美國貿易代表]]。大部分职业生涯在美国政府机关度过，2007年至2014年间在美国贸易代表署担任负责中国事务的重要律师，期间处理美国在[[世界贸易组织|世界贸易组织]]对中国提出的争端诉讼。她近年加入国会，曾担任[[美国众议院筹款委员会|众议院筹款委员会]]民主党首席贸易顾问<ref name=wsj201209>{{Cite news|author=Yuka Hayashi (林由佳)<!--駐DC日籍記者-->, Andrew Restuccia|date=2020-12-09|title=Biden to Name Katherine Tai U.S. Trade Representative|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/biden-to-name-katherine-tai-u-s-trade-representative-11607552856|access-date=2020-12-09|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211133632/https://www.wsj.com/articles/biden-to-name-katherine-tai-u-s-trade-representative-11607552856|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人背景 ==
戴琪生于美国[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]，能说流利的[[現代標準漢語|中文]]<ref name=udn201210>{{cite news|author=張文馨|url=https://udn.com/news/story/121687/5080696|title=父母來自台灣 戴琪將出任首位華裔貿易代表|date=2020-12-10|website=聯合新聞網|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210003452/https://udn.com/news/story/121687/5080696|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=|accessdate=2020-12-11}}</ref>。籍貫[[江蘇省_(中華民國)|江蘇]][[阜宁县|阜寧]]<ref>{{Cite web|author=李慈音|title=美貿易代表人選戴琪是國民黨軍統後代？ 身世之謎曝光|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201214002514-260407?chdtv|date=2020-12-14|website=中時新聞網|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216062415/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201214002514-260407?chdtv|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=|accessdate=}}</ref>，父母皆在[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]出生，於[[台灣|台灣]]成長，也皆於[[國立台灣大學|國立台灣大學]]畢業後留美[[归化|归化]]。父親於2019年摔倒意外逝世<ref name=twapple201211>{{cite news|author=林麒瑋|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201211/UVQWO2O3VRH65FQ6TC6OVEMS5Q/|title=【獨家】台裔戴琪將任美貿易代表 戴家栽培哈佛耶魯雙學霸秘訣曝光|date=2020-12-11|website=蘋果日報 (台灣)|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://archive.today/20201212155308/https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201211/UVQWO2O3VRH65FQ6TC6OVEMS5Q/|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=|accessdate=2020-12-12}}</ref>{{r|cna202014}}<ref>{{cite web|author=李昕、周上智|title=【戴琪14歲珍貴照】父親戴元亨生前寡言綽號「戴寡」 友人追憶60年情誼|url=https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=102347|access-date=|work=上報|date=2020-12-15|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215092415/https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=102347|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw}}</ref>，過去是{{le|華特·里德陸軍研究院|Walter Reed Army Institute of Research}}研究員，母親仍在[[國家衛生院_(美國)|國家衛生院]]做研究。她出生時父母尚未歸化，成為一家四口首位[[美國公民|美國公民]]<ref name=udn201212>{{cite news|author=胡夢瑋 (編譯)|others=|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6811/5086652|title=戴琪將任美貿易代表 接受提名演說中英版全文一次看|date=2020-12-12|website=聯合新聞網|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212151540/https://udn.com/news/story/6811/5086652|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=|accessdate=2020-12-12}}</ref>；在[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]长大并从{{le|希德威尔友谊学校|Sidwell Friends School}}毕业{{r|wsj201209}}，從小學到高中每個科目的成績都是A<ref name="cna202014"/>。畢業前，戴琪被[[耶魯大學|耶魯大學]]、[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]和[[加州理工學院|加州理工學院]]三所名校錄取，她選擇讀耶魯大學，因為戴琪的父親以及前美國總統[[喬治·赫伯特·華克·布希|喬治·赫伯特·華克·布希]]和[[比爾·柯林頓|比爾·柯林頓]]都曾經在該校就讀<ref name="cna202014"/>。個人拥有[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]]历史学[[文学士|文学士]]及[[哈佛法学院|哈佛法学院]][[法律博士|法律博士]]学位<ref name="waysandmeans">{{cite web|title=Neal Announces New Ways and Means Democratic Chief Trade Counsel|url=https://waysandmeans.house.gov/media-center/press-releases/neal-announces-new-ways-and-means-democratic-chief-trade-counsel|access-date=2020-12-09|publisher=House Ways and Means Committee|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211123149/https://waysandmeans.house.gov/media-center/press-releases/neal-announces-new-ways-and-means-democratic-chief-trade-counsel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1996年至1998年间，曾以[[雅礼协会|雅礼协会]][[讲师|讲师]]身份赴中国大陆<ref>{{cite web|author=|title=Katherine C. Tai*|work=Biennial Report 2003-2005|url=http://new.yalechina.org/docs/19.%20Biennial%20Report%202003-2005.pdf|access-date=|publisher=Yale-China Association (雅礼协会)|page=29|date=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212205318/http://new.yalechina.org/docs/19.%20Biennial%20Report%202003-2005.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=os>{{cite web|author=|title=Tai, Katherine|work=OpenSecrets.org|url=https://www.opensecrets.org/revolving/rev_summary.php?id=80604|access-date=2020-12-12|publisher=|page=|date=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212205342/https://www.opensecrets.org/revolving/rev_summary.php?id=80604|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在[[中山大学|中山大学]]教授英文{{r|udn201210}}<ref name="wanglynch">{{cite news |last1=Wang |first1=Amy B. |last2=Lynch |first2=David J. |title=Biden selects Katherine Tai as U.S. trade representative |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/12/09/biden-selects-katherine-tai-us-trade-representative/ |access-date=2020-12-10 |work=The Washington Post |date=2020-12-09 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211171045/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/12/09/biden-selects-katherine-tai-us-trade-representative/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。戴琪已婚住在[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|華盛頓特區]]{{r|twapple201211}}，父母因工作則定居[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]{{r|wj201210}}。

== 職務經歷 ==
學成後在數間法律事務所國際貿易部門及聯邦地區法院工作過{{r|os}}<ref>{{cite web|date=2019-01-22|title=Katherine Tai|url=https://www.uschina.org/katherine-tai|access-date=2020-12-09|publisher=US-China Business Council (美中贸易全国委员会)|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209225028/https://www.uschina.org/katherine-tai|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Gavin Bade |title=At USTR, a straight-shooter will have to navigate Biden's old guard in Washington |url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/02/01/katherine-tai-ustr-biden-463668 |access-date= |work=POLITICO |date=2021-02-01 |archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201150734/https://www.politico.com/news/2021/02/01/katherine-tai-ustr-biden-463668|dead-url=no|language=en-US}}</ref>，於2003年取得律師執業資格<ref>{{cite web|title=T - Active Attorneys|url=https://www.ca4.uscourts.gov/AttorneyBarAndECFStatus/rptN0046ActiveAttorneyst.pdf|page=2|date=2020-12-11|access-date=|publisher=United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212205318/https://www.ca4.uscourts.gov/AttorneyBarAndECFStatus/rptN0046ActiveAttorneyst.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年至2014年，受僱為聯邦政府一般律師（general attorney）擔任[[美國貿易代表處|美國貿易代表處]]顧問{{r|fp}}，期间于2011年至2014年出任对华贸易执法首席顾问（Chief Counsel for China Trade Enforcement）。2014年起任[[美国众议院筹款委员会|美国众议院筹款委员会]]贸易顾问，2017年升任首席贸易顾问<ref>{{cite news |last1=Merica |first1=Dan |last2=Saenz |first2=Arlette |last3=Zeleny |first3=Jeff |title=Biden expected to nominate Katherine Tai to serve as US Trade Representative |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/12/09/politics/katherine-tai-us-trade-representative/index.html |access-date=2020-12-09 |work=CNN |date=2020-12-09 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211200609/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/12/09/politics/katherine-tai-us-trade-representative/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年12月，媒体报道美国候任总统[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]计划提名戴琪为新任[[美国贸易代表|美国贸易代表]]{{r|wsj201209}}<ref>{{Cite news|last=Swanson|first=Ana|date=2020-12-09|title=Biden Picks Katherine Tai as Trade Representative|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/09/business/economy/katherine-tai-us-trade-representative.html|access-date=2020-12-09|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211143327/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/09/business/economy/katherine-tai-us-trade-representative.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在12月10日正式宣布<ref>{{cite press release |title=President-elect Biden Announces Key Members of His Administration |url=https://buildbackbetter.gov/press-releases/president-elect-biden-announces-key-members-of-his-administration/ |access-date=2020-12-10 |work=Biden-Harris Transition |date=2020-12-10 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211000943/https://buildbackbetter.gov/press-releases/president-elect-biden-announces-key-members-of-his-administration/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=rfa201210>{{cite news |author1=唐家婕 |title=拜登提名的贸易代表戴琪是谁? |url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/jt-12102020160424.html |work=自由亞洲電台|date=2020-12-10|access-date=2020-12-11|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210223128/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/jt-12102020160424.html|dead-url=no|language=zh-hans|via=}}</ref>。2021年3月17日，戴琪獲[[美國參議院|美國參議院]]以98票贊成、無人反對的壓倒性票數通過出任美國貿易代表<ref>{{cite web |title=將助拜登向中國問責!參議院全票通過台移民之女戴琪出任美貿易代表 |url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-03-18/550695 |publisher=新頭殼 |date=2021-03-18 |accessdate=2021-03-18 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2021-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319214429/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-03-18/550695 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，缺席的两位参议员[[伯尼·桑德斯|伯尼·桑德斯]]和[[廣野慶子|廣野慶子]]亦曾表示支持<ref>{{Cite news|author=Alex Rogers|date=2021-03-17|title=Senate confirms Katherine Tai to be US Trade Representative|language=en-US|work=CNN|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/17/politics/katherine-tai-trade-representative/index.html|access-date=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318212235/https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/17/politics/katherine-tai-trade-representative/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；隔天也是她生日，在副總統[[賀錦麗|賀錦麗]]見證下宣誓就職<ref>{{Cite web|author=Vice President Kamala Harris|title=It is critical our trade policies prioritize American workers and businesses. |url=https://www.facebook.com/VicePresident/posts/127147516034571|date=2021-03-18|accessdate=|website=|archive-date=2021-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331092423/https://m.facebook.com/VicePresident/posts/127147516034571 |dead-url=no |via=Facebook|language=en-US}}</ref><!-- https://twitter.com/VP/status/1372693574672867333 https://www.instagram.com/p/CMlCbycl8Pm/ 任職結束會存檔帳號改為"VP(最後屆期數字)"-->。

== 行事作風 ==
在[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院]]工作期間除美中貿易相關議題外，亦與眾議院議長[[南希·佩洛西|裴洛西]]辦公室、共同負責跟川普政府溝通修改《[[北美自由贸易协议|北美自貿協定]]》為《[[美墨加協定|美墨加協定]]》。當時平衡了[[工會|工會]]、[[環保團體|環保團體]]、企業[[遊說|遊說]]人士及川普政府等各方要求，即便相互牴觸，依然協助擬出讓參眾兩院壓倒性通過的協議，納入強化保護勞工與環境條款，參眾兩院議員因此對其表現印象深刻<ref name=edn201211>{{cite news|author= 林聰毅 (編譯)|url=https://money.udn.com/money/story/12937/5083878|title=【外媒綜合】美貿易代表戴琪何許人也？談判高手認清中國的挑戰|date=2020-12-11|website= 經濟日報 (台灣)|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213064848/https://money.udn.com/money/story/12937/5083878|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=|accessdate=2020-12-13}}</ref>。

有關美中貿易議題上，認為川普政府看來激進但本質上仍屬守勢，應增添攻勢手段，釐清讓美國、勞工、產業及盟友更加靈活的政策目標來提升競爭力，運用[[補貼|補貼]]等誘因以助降低美國對中國進口的過度依賴。由於能力備受肯定加上中文流利，可能採取[[世界贸易组织|世界贸易组织]]體系與盟友施壓策略{{r|edn201211}}，使中國方面不敢輕忽這美國貿易代表，網路上也大量轉載指戴琪比[[余茂春|余茂春]]更危險的文章{{r|rfa201210}}<ref>{{cite news|author=馮英志|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201211002182-260408?chdtv|title=戴琪任美貿易代表 陸網狂傳「她比川普華裔國師更狠」|date=2020-12-11|accessdate=2020-12-12|website=中時新聞網|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213085503/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201211002182-260408?chdtv|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=}}</ref>，甚至以訛傳訛是[[戴笠|戴笠]]後人<ref>{{cite news|author=呂佳蓉|url=https://udn.com/news/story/7331/5087789|title=戴琪是戴笠後人？陸網民：比余茂春更顯赫危險的人來了|date=2020-12-12|accessdate=2020-12-12|website=聯合新聞網|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213073810/https://udn.com/news/story/7331/5087789|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=|url=https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/4818 |title=【錯誤】網傳「拜登新任命的貿易代表戴琪是戴笠的曾孫女」、「戴琪是戴笠孫子戴以寬的女兒」？|date=2020-12-14|accessdate=2020-12-17|website=TFC|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217070618/https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/4818|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw|via=}}</ref>。

2021年3月，戴琪就任美國貿易代表後表示，短時間內不會取消向中國貨品[[特朗普关税|徵收關稅]]的措施，但對與中國進行[[中美贸易战|貿易談判]]持開放態度<ref>{{Cite web |title=戴琦：美國不準備取消中國貨關稅　但對談判持開放態度 |url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1583171-20210329.htm |accessdate=2021-03-29 |date=2021-03-29 |publisher=香港電台 |language=zh-hk |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515115547/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1583171-20210329.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

